{"tid":904174,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【低置仔和它們的產地】大家覺得香港Big 4住宅應該點排？","createTime":"2018-11-16T06:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T12:11:31.000Z","uid":163207,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0516939612191bb02a4b70dbdf3ab4a40a4a29ac","tid":904174,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"保升中心 ─ 著名地產商珅熊基出品,元祖Soho式住宅,用料上乘,坐落黃金葵●半山地段,惜樓齡較高及自殺案較多(多集中於282呎單位)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n瓏門 ─ 同為珅熊基出品,位處香港中心,於傳統高收入地區屯門仍為頂尖住宅,惜採用屏風樓設計,空氣質素較差,影響健康,不符合現代養生之主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兆康苑 ─ 初期居者有其屋屋苑,信心之選,鄰近西鐵站可直達金融中心屯門區,價格及租金有保證,唯不及屯門及葵●半山選址豪華,品位有別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屏欣苑 ─ 新晉居者有其屋屋苑,鄰近天水圍西鐵站,隱隱有挑戰霸主屯門區之勢,可惜被爆出不少用料及質素問題,出現信心危機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5184faae1c35788ad7d2ea22964bc1d059a6e28c","tid":904174,"uid":6624,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"你住邊"},{"pid":"6621b4ef3896b459ef28380afec5a400acd4377f","tid":904174,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hongkongpp.com/public/upload/880/1535905030sweethouse.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhongkongpp.com%2Fpublic%2Fupload%2F880%2F1535905030sweethouse.JPG&h=fe7fa413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb1e3a248b3bec5e6162ad933aed7bda3a41858","tid":904174,"uid":122377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5184faae1c35788ad7d2ea22964bc1d059a6e28c","tid":904174,"uid":6624,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"你住邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"我住邊關咩事？<br />\n利申：分身"},{"pid":"b7874bd17fdbbe185a3f40f513ed88fe7a6c6597"